Disqualified Erica has asked for forgiveness from her fans and viewers over her actions in a recent interview. The actress had hurled insults at Laycon and threatened to kill him before her disqualification. But she said: “I have apologised to the Housemates before leaving the House and I would like to apologize to everybody who watched the show, all my supporters, fans, my family, my friends. ” I am very sorry for my actions and I am very sorry for saying those horrible words to Laycon, Layton I do not hate you we have our disagreements but I don’t hate you and to everybody I insulted, Prince, Dora all the different people I insulted I’m very sorry.”